{
    "_comment": "Server flags per GPU type and model. GPU types match sgl-cookbook hardware IDs (b200, h200, h100, mi300x). TP/EP/DP values sourced from sgl-cookbook default configs. Tracing-specific flags (--disable-radix-cache, --enable-deterministic-inference) are passed via CLI, not stored here.",
